data.description: Welcome to your stunning like new home in Brunswick Forest. Situated on a coveted corner lot, this 2020 built residence epitomizes modern living with its open-concept design, featuring 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. The versatile finished room over garage adds flexibility, allowing you to tailor it to your needs - such as a home office, guest suite, or recreation room. Enjoy the charm of a covered front porch, providing a welcoming entry point to your new home. Enjoy outdoor living on the screened-in back porch, complete with 3-season windows for year-round enjoyment. A new paver walkway enhances accessibility and curb appeal, leading from the driveway to the back porch. The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, boasting a large island that serves as the focal point for gatherings and culinary needs. The primary suite offers a walk-in closet and a spa-like shower, creating a relaxing retreat within your own home. Admire the craftsmanship showcased throughout, with beautiful trim work adding a touch of elegance to every space. Enjoy the convenience of HOA-covered yard maintenance, allowing you plenty of time to enjoy this amenity-rich neighborhood, including parks, trails, and recreational facilities. Embrace the coastal NC lifestyle in a residence that effortlessly combines comfort and style. Your dream home awaits in Brunswick Forest!
